# MCP Quick Reference

**Config**: `~/.config/claude-code/mcp.json`
**Last Updated**: YYYY-MM-DD

## Available MCPs

### mem0 (port XXXX)
Persistent cross-session memory

```bash
# Add memory
Using mem0, add "Session summary..." with user_id [your-id]

# Search
Using mem0, search for "session handoff" with user_id [your-id]

# List recent
Using mem0, list memories for user_id [your-id] limit 10
```

**Example usage**:
```
# Store decision
Using mem0, add "Decision: [description]" with user_id [your-id]

# Recall patterns
Using mem0, search for "architecture decisions" with user_id [your-id]
```

