## Session Handoff Pattern

**End of session**:
```bash
Using mem0, add "Session YYYY-MM-DD: Completed X, Y, Z. Next: A, B, C. No blockers." with user_id [your-id]
```

**Start of session**:
```bash
Using mem0, search for "session handoff" with user_id [your-id] limit 3
```

